title: IIS7发布 EF MVC项目提示404.0页面错误解决方案
date: 2014-08-20 09:29:00
tags: IIS
categories: CSharp后端
---
[点击查看原文](https://www.cnblogs.com/bugzone/p/iisefmvc.html)

<div id="cnblogs_post_body" class="blogpost-body ">
    <p>之前服务器用的都是2003Server的服务器，发布mvc项目都没问题，今天换了一台机器，系统为Windows Server2008 R2&nbsp; 64位的发布mvc项目后就提示:</p>
<p><img src="https://images0.cnblogs.com/i/35314/201405/271107276031051.png" alt=""></p>
<p><span style="background-color: #ff0000;"><strong>一.</strong></span>服务器上安装MVC4.0安装程序 。下载地址：<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=30683" target="_blank">http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=30683</a></p>
<p>安装后在iis中是这样：</p>
<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""></p>
<p><span style="background-color: #ff0000;">二.</span>注册asp.net 4.0 到iis</p>
<div>
<p>32位的Windows：<br>---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>1. 运行-&gt;cmd&nbsp;</p>
<p>2. cd&nbsp; C:\Windows\Microsoft.NET\Framework\v4.0.30319</p>
<p>3. aspnet_regiis.exe -i</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>64位的Windows：<br>---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>1. 运行-&gt;cmd&nbsp;</p>
<p>2. cd &nbsp;C:\Windows\Microsoft.NET\Framework64\v4.0.30319</p>
<p>3. aspnet_regiis.exe -i</p>





</div>
<p><span style="background-color: #ff0000;"><strong>三.</strong></span>在web.config文件中添加modules runAllManagedModulesForAllRequests="true"配置项就能解决问题。</p>
<div class="cnblogs_Highlighter sh-gutter">
<div><div id="highlighter_274968" class="syntaxhighlighter  html"><div class="toolbar"><span><a href="#" class="toolbar_item command_help help">?</a></span></div><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="line number1 index0 alt2">1</div><div class="line number2 index1 alt1">2</div><div class="line number3 index2 alt2">3</div></td><td class="code"><div class="container"><div class="line number1 index0 alt2"><code class="html plain">&lt;</code><code class="html keyword">system.webServer</code><code class="html plain">&gt;</code></div><div class="line number2 index1 alt1"><code class="html spaces">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class="html plain">&lt;</code><code class="html keyword">modules</code> <code class="html plain">runAllManagedModulesForAllRequests="true"/&gt;</code></div><div class="line number3 index2 alt2"><code class="html plain">&lt;/</code><code class="html keyword">system.webServer</code><code class="html plain">&gt;</code></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
</div>
<p><span style="color: #888888; background-color: #ff0000;"><strong>四.</strong></span><span style="color: #000000;">配置对应的程序的“应用程序池”选择asp.net 4.0</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #888888; background-color: #ff0000;"><strong>五.</strong></span>如果是Windows Server2008 R2&nbsp;系统的问题。需要打补丁。</p>
<p>通过打了补丁之后问题解决。</p>
<p>官方补丁地址：<a href="http://support.microsoft.com/kb/980368" target="_blank">http://support.microsoft.com/kb/980368</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; 需要通过邮箱下载。</p>
<p>或者：<a href="http://files.cnblogs.com/liluping860122/407288_intl_x64_zip.rar" target="_blank">http://files.cnblogs.com/liluping860122/407288_intl_x64_zip.rar</a>&nbsp; 直接点击下载。</p>
